---
/**
 * MarkdownContent override — prototype `.prose` wrapper.
 *
 * Starlight's default wraps the body in `.sl-markdown-content` and imports
 * `style/markdown.css` (the default prose theme). This override swaps that for
 * the prototype `.prose` container styled by docs.css (headings, lede,
 * paragraphs, inline code, links, lists, etc.). The default markdown stylesheet
 * is deliberately not imported, so no Starlight prose styling leaks in.
 *
 * Heading `id`s emitted by Starlight's rehype pipeline are preserved on the
 * rendered `<h2>` / `<h3>` elements, which the prototype TOC scrollspy (docs.js)
 * binds to via `.toc ul a[href="#id"]`.
 */
---

<div class="prose"><slot /></div>
